                        <br/><br/><br/><h2>文 献</h2><br><ol><br><li id="R1"><span class='au'>Allen, C. D., Okada, T., Cyster, J. G.</span>: <span class="ti">Germinal-center organization and cellular dynamics.</span> <span class='so'>Immunity, 27, 190-202 (2007)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17723214" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R2"><span class='au'>Vinuesa, C. G., Sanz, I. & Cook, M. C.</span>: <span class="ti">Dysregulation of germinal centres in autoimmune disease.</span> <span class='so'>Nat. Rev. Immunol., 9, 845-857 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19935804" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R3"><span class='au'>Johnston, R. J., Poholek, A. C., DiToro, D. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Bcl6 and Blimp-1 are reciprocal and antagonistic regulators of T follicular helper cell differentiation.</span> <span class='so'>Science, 325, 1006-1010 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19608860" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R4"><span class='au'>Nurieva, R. I., Chung, Y., Martinez, G. J. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Bcl6 mediates development of T follicular helper T cells.</span> <span class='so'>Science, 325, 1001-1005 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19628815" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R5"><span class='au'>Yu, D., Rao, S. Tsai, L. M. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">The transcriptional repressor Bcl-6 directs T follicular helper cell lineage commitment.</span> <span class='so'>Immunity, 31, 457-468 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19631565" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R6"><span class='au'>Gatto, D., Paus, D., Basten, A. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Guidance of B cells by the orphan G protein-coupled receptor EBI2 shapes humoral immune responses.</span> <span class='so'>Immunity, 31, 259-269 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19615922" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</s